description._content: Original Collection: Harriet's Collection Item Number: HC1008 Image Description: George Peavy founded the arboretum, which would act as a laboratory for forestry students. The arboretum also contains the Forestry Club Cabin for club meetings. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
